import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

x = np.arange(-5,5,0.1)
y = np.tanh(x)
plt.plot(x,y, label="tanh")
plt.xlabel("X")
plt.ylabel("tanh(X)")
plt.title(" function tanh(X)")
plt.show()

%matplotlib inline
import matplotlib as mpl
mpl.rc('font', size=22)
from daft import PGM, Node, Plate
# Graphic design poser
asphalt= "#34495e"
pomengrante = "#c0392b"
westera = "#8e44ad"
belize = "#2980b9"
midnight = "#2c3e50"
model_style = {'ec': asphalt, 'lw': 3}
sp_style = {'ec': belize, 'lw': 3}
obs_style = {'ec': pomengrante, 'lw': 2}
edge_style = {"ec": midnight, 'lw': 2, 'head_width': 0.3}
plate_style = {'ec': midnight}

Latent Dirichlet Allocation¶

In [71]: 
pgm = PGM([8, 4], origin=[0, 0], observed_style='inner', grid_unit=4, node_unit=2.5)

pgm.add_node(Node("beta", r"$\beta$", 4.5, 2.5, plot_params=model_style))

pgm.add_node(Node("alpha", r"$\alpha$", 2, 1.5, plot_params=model_style))
pgm.add_node(Node("theta", r"$\theta$", 3, 1.5, plot_params=model_style))
pgm.add_node(Node("z", r"$z$", 4, 1.5, plot_params=model_style))
pgm.add_node(Node("w", r"$w$", 5, 1.5, plot_params=sp_style))
pgm.add_plate(Plate((2.5, 0.85, 3, 1.2), label=r"$M$", label_offset=[5, 20], shift=0, rect_params=plate_style))
pgm.add_plate(Plate((3.5, 0.95, 1.9, 1.0), label=r"$N$", label_offset=[5, 20], shift=0, rect_params=plate_style))
pgm.add_edge("beta", "w", plot_params=edge_style)
pgm.add_edge("alpha", "theta", plot_params=edge_style)
pgm.add_edge("theta", "z", plot_params=edge_style)
pgm.add_edge("z", "w", plot_params=edge_style)
